Rule (from kill-rekill-registry): every_kill_gets_rekill.
IP + threat only (no PIDs). Streams live Field attacks as each target is swallowed.

Sources:
  - NewLatest/.nexus-state/kill-rekill-registry.json
  - field-hostile.tsv, nexus-hostile.jsonl
  - boot-rekill validated IPs
  - dogshit permanent threats (pwnership)
  - hostile-ai-threats-seed

Live files for panel:
  - autopilot.json
  - live-feast.jsonl   (append each attack)
  - live-feed.json     (last N attacks, rewritten often)
"""
